<event name="FINISH_BEACON_HACKER">
	<preventQuest />
	<beaconType id="map_icon_exit_hacker" global="false">
		<color r="50" g="255" b="0" a="1" />
		<!--<unvisitedTooltip>This is the real exit beacon. Go here to travel to the next sector.</unvisitedTooltip>-->
		<visitedTooltip>这是真正的出口信标。</visitedTooltip>
	</beaconType>
	<variable name="loc_hacker_exit" op="set" val="1" />
	<text>你到达了星区出口...</text>
	<choice req="loc_hacker_exit" lvl="0" max_group="0" hidden="true" blue="false">
		<text>继续。</text>
		<event>
			<text>你似乎找到了出口，但你的星区数据集没能连接。有什么东西阻挡了信号......</text>
			<ship load="SHIP_HACKER_BROADCAST_FAKE" hostile="false" />
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>继续。</text>
				<event>
					<text>突然，你收到了来自一个隐藏在小卫星后面的广播空间站的呼救。"这是什么？那艘愚蠢的联邦小飞船想离开？恐怕我不能允许这样做！"</text>	
					<ship hostile="true" />
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>继续。</text>
						<event load="COMBAT_CHECK" />
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice req="loc_hacker_exit" lvl="1" max_group="0" hidden="true" blue="false"> <!--theoretically you can never get this except in the fleet so Im just going to make it that for simplisities sake-->
		<text>继续。</text>
		<event>
			<text>黑客空间站已经被击败，但叛军舰队已经控制了信标！你必须奋起直追。你必须为你的出路而战！</text>
			<customFleet right="false" firing="true" autoDarkening="false">CUSTOM_FLEET_REBEL</customFleet>
			<ship load="SHIP_REBEL_FLEET_S" hostile="true" />
			<environment type="PDS" target="player" />
			<noASBPlanet />
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>继续。</text>
				<event load="COMBAT_CHECK" />
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true" req="engines" lvl="6">
				<text>(先进引擎)尝试逃离精英舰。</text>
				<event load="FLEET_ESCAPE" />
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_CREW_JERRY">
				<text>(杰瑞)"你好！"</text>
				<event>
					<text load="TEXT_ENCOUNTER_REBEL_JERRY_HELLO" />
					<ship hostile="false" /> 
				</event>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>
<event name="HACKER_EXIT_DEFEAT">
	<text>黑客空间站已经被打败了。幸运的是，一旦黑客的威胁被消除，你的星区数据集就会连接到出口信标。</text>
	<variable name="loc_hackerexit" op="set" val="1" />
	<autoReward level="HIGH">standard</autoReward>
</event>
